quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,"Day ur twalav ara wid ineûfen l$it n Öebbi, s tijehli? Ssersen agdud nnsen deg uxxam n twa$it"
  14,29,"Loahennama ad ô$en degs: a yir leqôaô"
  14,30,"Gan aS i Öebbi tanudda, iwakken ad telfen seg ubrid iS. Ini: \"zzhut! S tidep, leqôaô nnwen d times"
  14,31,"Ini i imdanen iW iumnen, ad bedden i téallit, ad seddqen seg wayen iten N$at, s tuffra u âinani, uqbel a d ias wass ideg ur illi ssuq, ur telli tdukli"
  14,32,"Öebbi i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan, id Isse$layen aman seg igenni, Issufu$ ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Inub fellawen s isaffen, u s lbabuô i iteddun di yill, s lameô iS"
  14,33,"Inub fellawen s yiîij d waggur, d imezgiyen. Inub fellawen s yiv akked wass"
  14,34,"Ifka yawen seg wayen akw i S tessutrem. Ma pêesbem l$it n Mass nnwen, ur tessawavem. Ih, amdan, s tidep, d amednus, d ajehli"